<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77681fcf-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s410aaa–57"><num value="410aaa–57">§ 410aaa–57.</num><heading> Acquired lands to be made part of Mojave National Preserve</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Any lands acquired by the Secretary under this part shall become part of the Mojave National Preserve.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77681fd0-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/103/433/tV/s517">Pub. L. 103–433, title V, § 517</ref>, <date date="1994-10-31">Oct. 31, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/4495">108 Stat. 4495</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
